When justice is bloodshed, warriors rise. Samurai Fury (aka Muromachi Outsiders) is the electrifying new historical action drama of 2025—with lightning-fast swordplay, fierce rebellions, and unforgettable characters.

🩸 DUST BUNNY – Official Trailer (2025) | Horror Thriller 🩸
Some monsters hide under the bed... and some fight back. Dust Bunny is the wildly inventive horror thriller debuting in 2025, where nightmares and assassins collide in a dark, memorable tale.

Film Overview:
When an 8-year-old girl named Aurora is convinced a monster stole her family, she hires an unlikely protector—her mysterious next-door neighbor, a hitman for hire. He may be the only one capable of confronting the darkness... but secrets make him just as deadly.

Cast:
Mads Mikkelsen
Sigourney Weaver
Sophie Sloan as Aurora
David Dastmalchian

Directed by Bryan Fuller (feature film debut)
Release Info: Premiering at Toronto International Film Festival — Midnight Madness (Sept 9, 2025). Theatrical release in U.S. on December 5.
